WEBVTT

00:02.250 --> 00:04.070
<i>So tell me how this works.</i>

00:04.188 --> 00:05.990
<i>I'm awake with my
wife, and I close my eyes.</i>

00:06.024 --> 00:07.241
<i>I open them.</i>

00:07.292 --> 00:08.576
<i>I'm awake with my son.</i>

00:08.627 --> 00:11.078
And this has been happening
since the accident?

00:12.747 --> 00:16.166
<i>So you begin working on
one case here in reality,</i>

00:16.200 --> 00:18.836
<i>and then, suddenly,</i>
<i>you begin working another case</i>

00:18.870 --> 00:20.804
<i>there, in your dream.</i>

00:20.839 --> 00:23.007
<i>It all feels
completely real to me.</i>

00:23.041 --> 00:25.092
You can't tell whether
you're awake or asleep

00:25.143 --> 00:26.176
at this very moment?

00:26.210 --> 00:27.261
<i>Well, I can assure you,</i>

00:27.312 --> 00:29.146
Detective Britten,
this is not a dream.

00:29.180 --> 00:31.765
That's exactly what
the other shrink said.

00:33.865 --> 00:35.965
AWAKE
S01 Ep 03 - Guilty

